</span></p><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-118_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-ef478cbf-5a49-46b3-89c6-009c0fc542ee"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Key features include:


